{"tid":2418300,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味 外賣叫咗我蠔餅 佢自動同我走晒啲蠔","createTime":"2021-02-22T13:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:48:54.000Z","uid":116526,"like":1461,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"7125d608f745455c554930f6f2694cdb0ce9d728","tid":2418300,"uid":116526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n今日係公司OT，叫咗個碟頭飯，見個市跌成咁，就叫多個蠔餅諗住安慰下自己<br />\n好啦，嚟到時候見到個盒 咦？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmfYxUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmfYxUK.jpg&h=2a3bd519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一打開，屌你老母！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2sgjzW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2sgjzW.jpg&h=ec75fa6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n乜蠔餅係咁撚樣架咩？？？啲蠔唔撚見晒？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我叫蠔餅你同我走蠔 咁我食乜撚野？<br />\n你賣晒打比我同我講無都好呀，你就咁整隻煎強收我$100有無撚野呀？？？<br />\n之後睇返個盒先知，佢明知自己無蠔都照煎pat強就出貨比我<br />\n咁同詐騙有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時食一個碟頭飯都覺得好貴，家陣第一次加餸就咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">上環 明記飯店 foodpanda叫</span>"},{"pid":"e87b11ab1f0d7eea617fd1f0728419829ae4102d","tid":2418300,"uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1845e3af61f996ba8afc2ac16442d2a4dd931bba","tid":2418300,"uid":16061,"like":552,"dislike":1,"score":551,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"上完lihkg屌